  "detailed_description": "<strong>Trapped In Stone</strong> is a cinematic linear World War 2 Horror Game where you play as A German Officer who gets trapped inside a bunker by American troops. Explore the bunker, find a way out and fight for your life.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880980/extras/0c1cae9c3a22ea85a6ece1f8737157ba.poster.avif?t=1646244975\" width=624 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880980/extras/0c1cae9c3a22ea85a6ece1f8737157ba.webm?t=1646244975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880980/extras/0c1cae9c3a22ea85a6ece1f8737157ba.mp4?t=1646244975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>Trapped In Stone offers a unique <strong>non-repetitive gameplay.</strong> It takes inspirations from various genres.<br>-Explore the claustrophobic bunker (which is based on real location).<br>-Fight off human and non-human enemies<br>-Get immersed in the story with the help of high quality cinematics.<br>-Beat various mini-games in order to progress through the story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880980/extras/ffe52300a60754223267b09f4d712cd5.poster.avif?t=1646244975\" width=624 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880980/extras/ffe52300a60754223267b09f4d712cd5.webm?t=1646244975\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1880980/extras/ffe52300a60754223267b09f4d712cd5.mp4?t=1646244975\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story.</h2>You play as Officer Manfred - A German WW2 Officer trapped inside a bunker. Looking for a way out, you soon discover an American war weapon that threatens to kill all of the human population.",
